    - `write_binary_int{16,32,64}_{le,be}/3`, `write_binary_int{16,32,64}_{le,be}/4`
    - `read_binary_int8/[34]`
    - `read_binary_uint8/[34]`
    - `putback_int8/[34]`
    - `putback_uint8/[34]`
    - `read_binary_int{16,32,64}/3`, `read_binary_int{16,32,64}/4`
